---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Minus One Labs" description="Minus One Labs was founded to help local small businesses get a professional online presence fast, affordably, and without the technical hassle.">
  <Navbar />
  <div class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0a2540] to-[#1a0033] min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 text-[#635bff] text-sm font-medium px-5 py-2 rounded-3xl mb-6">
          Founded 2020
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-semibold leading-tight mb-6">
          Built for the businesses<br />that build communities.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-zinc-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We exist to make a professional online presence accessible to every local business — not just the ones with big budgets.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Story -->
      <div class="bg-[#1a3a66] border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-5">Our Story</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Minus One Labs was founded in 2020 by a developer who kept watching the same frustrating pattern repeat itself: local small businesses — restaurants, contractors, salons, consultants — were either stuck with no website, a broken WordPress site from 2014, or paying $5,000+ to agencies that took months to deliver something generic.
          </p>
          <p>
            The problem wasn't demand. Every small business <em>wants</em> a professional online presence. The problem was access — it was too slow, too expensive, and too technical.
          </p>
          <p>
            So we built a better way. A productized service that takes a business from zero to live in 14 days, with everything included: design, hosting, SEO, lead capture, and ongoing support. No coding required. No hidden fees. No waiting months for a freelancer to disappear.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission + Values -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10">
        <div class="bg-[#1a3a66] border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🎯</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Get your business online in just 14 days with a fast, modern, SEO-optimized one-page website — fully built, hosted, and managed for you, with no coding required.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1a3a66] border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Who We Serve</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Local small businesses — restaurants, contractors, salons, consultants, and more — who want a high-quality website and lead-generation system without the hassle or high cost of traditional web agencies.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1a3a66] border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">⚡</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Why We're Different</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We use modern tooling (Astro + Cloudflare) that makes sites blazing fast at near-zero hosting cost. That efficiency gets passed directly to our clients — premium results at accessible prices.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1a3a66] border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">📈</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Built to Grow With You</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Every site we build is a foundation, not a ceiling. Phase 2 features — client portals, booking, reviews — are already in development and will be available as your business scales.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/#contact" class="bg-[#635bff] hover:bg-[#7e6bfd] px-10 py-4 rounded-3xl text-lg font-semibold transition inline-block">
          Start Your Project
        </a>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mt-4">Free quote · Reply within 24 hours · No commitment</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
